name: A Supercomputer's Dilemma
description:
I'm so sorry for this piece of crap, this is my first real game, and I had to cut a lot of stuff out. Nonetheless, I hope you enjoy somehow. This was a submission to Mini Jam 65 and the theme was "Abandoned." I think I put a nice twist on it. Please play to the end for the full experience.

Instructions: A and D to move and W to jump. E to pick up the crates.

By the way, huge thanks to GDG^meplayer for supporting me and helping me program through the weekend--I wouldn't have been able to do this without him.
